REFERRED TO HOUSING, CONSTRUCTION AND COMMUNITY DEVELOPMENT

Title: Directs the division of housing and community renewal to study non-rental fees charged by landlords
Summary: Directs the division of housing and community renewal to study non-rental fees charged by landlords and report to the legislature.
ActClause: AN ACT directing the division of housing and community renewal to study non-rental fees charged by landlords
